Use the standard library
This is how to mean_absolute_deviation of numbers:
  Remember that total is 0.000000
  Do this numbers's length times:
    Remember that i is diff of numbers's length and numbers's length
    Increase i by 1
  End do
  Remember that i is 0
  Do this numbers's length times:
    Remember that total is sum of total and item i in numbers
    Increase i by 1
  End do
  Remember that mean is quotient of total and numbers's length
  Remember that deviation_total is 0.000000
  Remember that i is 0
  Do this numbers's length times:
    Remember that deviation_total is sum of deviation_total and abs of diff of item i in numbers and mean
    Increase i by 1
  End do
  The answer is quotient of deviation_total and numbers's length
